title: World of Warcraft
description:
World of Warcraft, thc, and all patches to get you to what this realm is running. http://www.wow-ps.com


We need players, just starting out and would like to see some more enter and play at Power Server. Please visit the site you will get all the info and ideas about the realm. Also read the poll i have put up there. Having a decision problem just want to hear it from the players.

Come and join us in lots of fun and fast leveling, you will not be disappointed.

www.wow-ps.com has become wrath of lich king so when you are done installing this and patching you can download the wrath of lich king and install it right over your world of warcraft folder. it automatically installs right into the folder then you patch twice after that. you prefer not to play at wrath of lich king and would rather play thc expansion then you can go to www.samcclive.com and create an account there. samcclive is a fun realm also. go check out the site and decide. i hope you all enjoy playing. hope to see you there.
